column21: DV_ is the dependent variable traditionally associated with this data set

Public data, downloaded from https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/wine+quality.  Originally published by Cortez et al. (2009) https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0167923609001377?via%3Dihub

Public data, downloaded from https://osf.io/23nzu/. Originally published by Martin et al. (2021) https://www.researchgate.net/publication/354992641_The_visual_arrays_task_Visual_storage_capacity_or_attention_control.

SymSpan = Memory for sequences of spatial information. RunSpatial = Memory for most-recently presented spatial information. VisualArrays = Recognition of change in visually presented information. Antisaccade = Attention control test that requires suppression of reflexive eye movements.
